579
00:32:33,029 --> 00:32:33,851
Come back here.

580
00:32:34,759 --> 00:32:35,797
Ja-Oh!

581
00:32:38,042 --> 00:32:39,141
Help me.

582
00:32:44,490 --> 00:32:46,490
Happy Valentine’s.

583
00:32:49,714 --> 00:32:51,714
Happy Valentine’s.

584
00:32:53,351 --> 00:32:54,553
Thank you.

585
00:32:56,361 --> 00:32:57,604
I’m back.

586
00:32:58,193 --> 00:33:01,956
