599
00:33:34,113 --> 00:33:36,143
You said you were going to help your sister.

600
00:33:38,187 --> 00:33:39,228
Here, put it down here.

601
00:33:39,228 --> 00:33:40,229
There we go.

602
00:33:43,566 --> 00:33:44,712
This is cute.

603
00:34:01,653 --> 00:34:02,527
This is cute.

604
00:34:19,960 --> 00:34:21,223
So cute.

605
00:34:22,541 --> 00:34:24,213
Let me put my stuff away.

606
00:34:25,204 --> 00:34:26,897
Are you the Valentine’s Day star?

607
00:34:28,344 --> 00:34:29,513
Here, careful not to drop it.

608
00:34:29,513 --> 00:34:30,204
Thank you.

609
00:34:30,884 --> 00:34:32,091
Do you want my sister to be impressed?

610
00:34:32,316 --> 00:34:33,724
Do you know J’Rock?

611
00:34:33,724 --> 00:34:35,282
Are you sure you know what J’Rock is?

612
00:34:35,282 --> 00:34:38,213
Not only J’Rock, I also know JJ.

613
00:34:38,213 --> 00:34:39,231
Who’s JJ?

614
00:34:39,313 --> 00:34:42,044
JJ, the son of Joom who sells Jim-Joom at the Jarket.

615
00:34:42,044 --> 00:34:42,680
Market!

616
00:34:57,859 --> 00:35:00,668
