00:35:08,860 --> 00:35:09,984
Tong came second!

623
00:35:09,984 --> 00:35:10,686
Yay!

624
00:35:11,061 --> 00:35:13,061
That’s amazing.

625
00:35:16,272 --> 00:35:19,503
Tong got the second place.

626
00:35:19,503 --> 00:35:22,340
From the last to the second place.

627
00:35:22,774 --> 00:35:24,774
That’s a leap.

628
00:35:24,774 --> 00:35:28,653
Unlike yours, she used to come first and now she’s still the first.

629
00:35:28,796 --> 00:35:30,796
