631
00:35:38,465 --> 00:35:39,169
Ping.

632
00:35:41,901 --> 00:35:44,058
You’re here as well?

633
00:35:44,783 --> 00:35:45,440
Yes.

634
00:35:52,847 --> 00:35:53,596
Hey.

635
00:35:53,719 --> 00:35:56,915
That year we had the beauty pageant, I was having diarrhea.

636
00:35:56,915 --> 00:35:58,677
Otherwise, I’d have won.

637
00:35:58,997 --> 00:36:00,452
You’d have been the second.

638
00:36:01,584 --> 00:36:05,590
It was a relief you had diarrhea, otherwise, I wouldn't have won.

639
00:36:06,058 --> 00:36:06,672
Thank you.

640
00:36:06,672 --> 00:36:07,498
Yeah.

641
00:36:12,027 --> 00:36:13,291
Well, Yong.

642
00:36:14,807 --> 00:36:15,839
Would you like to switch?

643
00:36:18,128 --> 00:36:20,819
Hey, we can’t switch.

644
00:36:20,819 --> 00:36:23,754
Our son is so good, why would you want to switch?

645
00:36:23,883 --> 00:36:25,268
I meant the wife.

646
00:36:26,480 --> 00:36:28,283
Tao, you bastard.

647
00:36:28,283 --> 00:36:29,448
I’m, your wife.

648
00:36:29,448 --> 00:36:32,358
People all over the town wanted to have me.

649
00:36:32,836 --> 00:36:33,760
You…!

650
00:36:34,836 --> 00:36:36,503
Well, he deserves a kick.

651
00:36:37,526 --> 00:36:40,240
He never changes, just like that from when he was a young boy until old.

652
00:36:40,592 --> 00:36:42,592
