654
00:36:46,619 --> 00:36:48,619
Shall I take you to J’Phon’s Milk Place?

655
00:36:50,155 --> 00:36:50,831
Let’s go.

656
00:36:52,447 --> 00:36:53,230
Oh?

657
00:36:53,503 --> 00:36:55,957
What are you girls talking about?

658
00:36:56,622 --> 00:36:59,014
Let’s go home, Ton Liu.

659
00:36:59,875 --> 00:37:01,729
You can head home first, Mom and Dad.

660
00:37:02,147 --> 00:37:04,751
I’ll take Ton Liu to J’Phon’s Milk Place.

661
00:37:07,040 --> 00:37:08,222
I’ll take her home.

662
00:37:08,936 --> 00:37:10,385
Take good care of your sister.

663
00:37:10,853 --> 00:37:13,800
Sure, I will take good care of her.

664
00:37:13,800 --> 00:37:15,096
Don’t stay out too late.

665
00:37:15,096 --> 00:37:16,046
Sure, Mom.

666
00:37:16,046 --> 00:37:17,212
I’ll see you at home.

667
00:37:17,680 --> 00:37:18,300
Let’s go.

668
00:37:18,525 --> 00:37:19,565
Here, Papa.

669
00:37:23,005 --> 00:37:24,804
What should we eat, Ton Liu?

670
00:37:25,007 --> 00:37:26,125
Just say it to your sister.

671
00:37:26,740 --> 00:37:28,238
I’ll have everything.

672
00:37:28,730 --> 00:37:29,960
Everything?

673
00:37:31,141 --> 00:37:34,569
I was thinking of Kaya Toast and Milk with syrup.

674
00:37:34,791 --> 00:37:35,643
Do you want that too?

675
00:37:35,643 --> 00:37:36,297
Yes.

676
00:37:41,441 --> 00:37:42,171
Give me a minute.

677
00:37:46,724 --> 00:37:47,908
You’re good.

678
00:37:47,908 --> 00:37:49,034
You came second.

679
00:37:50,511 --> 00:37:52,417
I know I lost, you don’t have to rub it on me.

680
00:37:53,672 --> 00:37:54,625
What do you want me to do?

681
00:37:56,323 --> 00:37:57,417
What to do?

682
00:37:58,155 --> 00:38:00,453
What should it be?

683
00:38:01,063 --> 00:38:02,092
Should I shave?

684
00:38:03,052 --> 00:38:05,442
Or I can do a buzz cut if you want.

685
00:38:06,057 --> 00:38:07,368
Why the haircut?

686
00:38:07,737 --> 00:38:08,915
Can’t it be anything else?

687
00:38:11,426 --> 00:38:13,247
That’s because I bet on a haircut with you.

688
00:38:15,918 --> 00:38:17,106
Or do you want money?

689
00:38:17,425 --> 00:38:18,587
I don’t have any money.

690
00:38:18,587 --> 00:38:21,385
Hey, Tong! What sort of person do you think I am?

691
00:38:24,216 --> 00:38:25,471
Then what do you want me to do?

692
00:38:26,849 --> 00:38:28,306
You don’t have to do anything for me.

693
00:38:29,315 --> 00:38:31,305
I actually got what I wanted from you.

694
00:38:32,067 --> 00:38:32,688
Huh?

695
00:38:34,263 --> 00:38:35,007
What’s that?

696
00:38:35,007 --> 00:38:35,862
Lin!

697
00:38:36,937 --> 00:38:39,706
Mr. Sommai wanted to see me, can you come alone?

698
00:38:40,124 --> 00:38:40,889
Sure.

699
00:38:41,874 --> 00:38:43,120
Ton Liu, I’ll be right back.

700
00:38:44,658 --> 00:38:45,378
Lin.

701
00:38:45,698 --> 00:38:46,483
Lin, Lin.

702
00:38:46,483 --> 00:38:47,559
What is it? Tell me before you go.

703
00:38:47,682 --> 00:38:48,317
Lin!

704
00:38:51,265 --> 00:38:51,990
Lin!

705
00:38:56,002 --> 00:38:57,848
Do you want my sister to be impressed?

706
00:39:02,205 --> 00:39:03,032
What is it, little one?

707
00:39:03,770 --> 00:39:05,284
Do you know J’Rock?

708
00:39:10,723 --> 00:39:11,689
A snack?

709
00:39:13,560 --> 00:39:14,888
J’Rock!

710
00:39:15,567 --> 00:39:16,949
You’re doing that as if it’s some soy sauce.

711
00:39:17,244 --> 00:39:18,269
I want it J’Rock.

712
00:39:18,269 --> 00:39:19,589
Problems.

713
00:39:19,589 --> 00:39:20,324
Do you mean, “No problem”?

714
00:39:20,595 --> 00:39:21,279
Thanks for the correction.

715
00:39:22,053 --> 00:39:23,606
Are you sure you know what J’Rock is?

716
00:39:23,606 --> 00:39:25,877
You’re looking down on me, boy.

717
00:39:26,000 --> 00:39:29,916
Not only J’Rock, I also know JJ.

718
00:39:29,916 --> 00:39:30,917
Who’s JJ?

719
00:39:31,237 --> 00:39:33,967
JJ, the son of Joom who sells Jim-Joom at the Jarket.

720
00:39:33,967 --> 00:39:35,110
Market!

721
00:39:35,110 --> 00:39:36,884
Come on, Uncle. It’s J’Rock.

722
00:39:36,884 --> 00:39:37,775
Right, right.

723
00:39:37,775 --> 00:39:38,400
You’d better get it straight.

724
00:39:38,400 --> 00:39:39,297
Don’t worry.

725
00:39:39,297 --> 00:39:40,176
Leave it to me.

726
00:39:55,008 --> 00:39:55,827
Tong!

727
00:39:57,181 --> 00:39:58,657
I don’t owe you anything anymore.

728
00:40:02,492 --> 00:40:04,270
What’s with your hair?

729
00:40:04,499 --> 00:40:05,697
And what’s this costume?

730
00:40:05,697 --> 00:40:06,499
Well,

731
00:40:07,763 --> 00:40:08,902
you like J’Rock, don’t you?

732
00:40:10,280 --> 00:40:11,127
The little one told me that.

733
00:40:14,474 --> 00:40:15,882
So awesome.

734
00:40:21,371 --> 00:40:22,236
Why are you laughing?

735
00:40:28,980 --> 00:40:30,555
You got played.

736
00:40:31,638 --> 00:40:32,621
Little one!

737
00:40:33,507 --> 00:40:35,290
I was bleaching it for hours.

738
00:40:35,290 --> 00:40:36,708
My scalp was all burning.

739
00:40:37,446 --> 00:40:39,126
This jacket is so hot.

740
00:40:41,666 --> 00:40:43,006
These pants are so tight.

741
00:40:43,326 --> 00:40:46,248
People were staring at me when I was driving down the street.

742
00:40:46,445 --> 00:40:47,718
That’s pretty awesome though, Tong.

743
00:40:47,940 --> 00:40:49,432
So awesome.

744
00:41:01,862 --> 00:41:02,778
Hey!

745
00:41:03,270 --> 00:41:05,285
Stop playing with my hair.

746
00:41:06,342 --> 00:41:07,183
Tong.

747
00:41:07,454 --> 00:41:10,047
Whichever devil’s gotten into you that made you do this hair?

748
00:41:10,047 --> 00:41:10,773
Right.

749
00:41:11,191 --> 00:41:14,466
Oh, you must have tried to copy Sakuraki.

750
00:41:16,410 --> 00:41:17,453
Me?

751
00:41:20,209 --> 00:41:21,316
I’m cooler than that, of course.

752
00:41:21,316 --> 00:41:22,714
My ass.

753
00:41:23,231 --> 00:41:24,638
Aren’t you afraid of Sommai?

754
00:41:25,623 --> 00:41:26,774
Why would I be?

755
00:41:27,069 --> 00:41:31,400
If someone like me were to get my hair colored, everyone in school has to know.

756
00:41:31,843 --> 00:41:32,628
My ass.

757
00:41:33,071 --> 00:41:34,193
What do you mean you’re not scared?

758
00:41:34,193 --> 00:41:35,928
I saw you sitting in the toilet since 5 AM.

759
00:41:37,971 --> 00:41:39,040
Such a sucker.

760
00:41:39,581 --> 00:41:40,291
Pao!

761
00:41:41,275 --> 00:41:42,007
What is it?

762
00:41:45,007 --> 00:41:46,248
What is it?

763
00:42:04,927 --> 00:42:10,894
