764
00:42:12,817 --> 00:42:14,497
(when she actually won the bet.)

765
00:42:19,976 --> 00:42:20,820
Tong!

766
00:42:22,002 --> 00:42:22,961
Shit!

767
00:42:24,587 --> 00:42:26,267
What did you do to your hair?

768
00:42:27,542 --> 00:42:28,875
Tong’s done for.

769
00:42:28,875 --> 00:42:30,781
This is my natural hair color, Sir.

770
00:42:34,170 --> 00:42:36,426
