771
00:42:36,426 --> 00:42:37,347
I trust you now, Mai.

772
00:42:37,347 --> 00:42:37,882
Trust me on what?

773
00:42:37,882 --> 00:42:39,382
He wouldn’t be able to catch up.

774
00:42:41,179 --> 00:42:45,164
(From then on, I wanted to study hard)

775
00:42:45,705 --> 00:42:49,922
(because I knew that it’s what made Lin happy.)

776
00:42:50,882 --> 00:42:52,089
You’re still smiling, are you?

777
00:42:53,467 --> 00:42:55,770
Buy me a new shoe polish, understand?

778
00:42:56,270 --> 00:42:57,247
Do you understand?

779
00:42:57,715 --> 00:42:58,738
Turn this way.

780
00:43:00,497 --> 00:43:02,005
No one’s as naughty as you are.

781
00:43:02,329 --> 00:43:03,738
You’re the most naughty one in the 3 realms.

782
00:43:04,903 --> 00:43:06,288
Here.

783
00:43:10,007 --> 00:43:11,581
I think the reason why Lin cut her hair short

784
00:43:12,467 --> 00:43:14,060
is because she has feelings for me.

785
00:43:15,340 --> 00:43:16,572
Oh, Lin.

786
00:43:16,966 --> 00:43:18,693
Why didn’t you just tell me you like me?

787
00:43:19,185 --> 00:43:19,887
What?

788
00:43:20,330 --> 00:43:25,252
It’s obvious that Lin cut her hair short to please me.

789
00:43:25,252 --> 00:43:26,309
Huh?

790
00:43:26,847 --> 00:43:28,534
Lin likes me.

791
00:43:28,854 --> 00:43:29,816
Huh?

792
00:43:29,816 --> 00:43:30,703
What are you ‘Huh’-ing for?

793
00:43:32,721 --> 00:43:35,700
Shall we just ask Lin why she cut her hair short?

794
00:43:35,700 --> 00:43:36,727
Let’s do it.

795
00:43:38,105 --> 00:43:38,682
Come on.

796
00:43:38,682 --> 00:43:39,412
Lin,

797
00:43:40,963 --> 00:43:42,317
we have something to ask you.

798
00:43:44,507 --> 00:43:45,352
What is it?

799
00:43:45,746 --> 00:43:48,988
We were wondering why you decided to cut your hair short.

800
00:43:49,776 --> 00:43:50,669
That’s right, that’s right.

801
00:43:50,669 --> 00:43:51,425
Oh.

802
00:43:51,425 --> 00:43:52,790
Right.

803
00:43:58,451 --> 00:43:59,541
It’s fine.

804
00:43:59,861 --> 00:44:03,167
You don’t have to answer, I do understand.

805
00:44:03,885 --> 00:44:07,662
