806
00:44:08,400 --> 00:44:10,014
I like you too, Lin.

807
00:44:10,802 --> 00:44:11,868
Ew.

808
00:44:12,139 --> 00:44:12,786
What’s up with you?

809
00:44:13,795 --> 00:44:15,917
Do you all have a narcissistic complex?

810
00:44:16,631 --> 00:44:19,340
I didn't know it was contagious.

811
00:44:19,487 --> 00:44:22,613
And what’s wrong with that, Giraffe?

812
00:44:22,736 --> 00:44:24,448
Do you want to get kicked by a Giraffe, Mai?

813
00:44:24,448 --> 00:44:25,274
Hey!

814
00:44:25,274 --> 00:44:26,051
Ja-Oh!

815
00:44:26,051 --> 00:44:27,007
Help!

816
00:44:27,007 --> 00:44:28,599
Lin!

817
00:44:28,771 --> 00:44:31,892
Can I ask you frankly?

818
00:44:32,190 --> 00:44:35,549
Why did you cut your hair?

819
00:44:39,561 --> 00:44:41,511
I cut my hair because…

820
00:44:41,511 --> 00:44:42,788
Because…

821
00:44:43,871 --> 00:44:44,753
Because…

822
00:44:45,007 --> 00:44:46,978
Because…

823
00:44:49,341 --> 00:44:51,046
Because short hair is trendy right now

824
00:44:51,415 --> 00:44:53,144
and I wanted to switch up my look a little.

825
00:44:53,144 --> 00:44:53,906
What do you think?

826
00:44:53,906 --> 00:44:54,552
Is it nice?

827
00:44:54,552 --> 00:44:55,371
Yeah.

828
00:44:56,367 --> 00:44:57,752
